{"type": "article", "id": 23102, "title": "金属框架椅子", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-02T07:30:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110536179H5kp0ScTXeJ36.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是瑞典家具公司 Göhlin 推出的 Steel 系列，有两款。椅腿和扶手几乎由一条极细的金属框架构成，流畅的曲线让椅子显得简洁轻盈，是极简金属风格。另一款在椅子在靠背、座位和扶手上采用了皮垫，但金属结构依然保留了下来，是向舒适性的改进。<a href=\"http://steelbygohlin.se/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110534xSVzC68aWDyLtiEU.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.47457627\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110535kf5tqgD1zbmaGl09.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021105350DipIto9g2NP1XjA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110536hPd1Q2fJBpbKwaZo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}